#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:89
msgid "Any information you provide will not be shared with service providers without your authorization."
msgstr "Nobena informacija ne bo deljena s ponudnikom storitve brez tvoje avtorizacije."

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:88
msgid "You may need to first sign up for an account with the service that you plan to use. When you do so, you would need to authorize Contact Form 7 to access the service with your account."
msgstr "Pred uporabo servisa, ki ga nameravaš uporabljat, se moraš naprej prijavit v račun. Nato s svojim računom avtoriziraš Contact Form 7 za dostop do servisa."

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:87
msgid "On this screen, you can manage services that are available through Contact Form 7. Using API will allow you to collaborate with any services that are available."
msgstr "Na dotičnemu zaslonu lahko upravljaš storitve, ki so na voljo preko Contact Form 7. Z uporabo API vmesnika, lahko sodeluješ s katerimkoli servisom, ki je na voljo."

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:84
msgid "A mail-tag is also a short code enclosed in square brackets that you can use in every Mail and Mail (2) field. A mail-tag represents a user input value through an input field of a corresponding form-tag."
msgstr "Poštna oznaka je prav tako kratka koda zaprta v oglate oklepaje in jo lahko uporabite v vsakem Pošta in Pošta (2) polju. Poštna oznaka (mail-tag) predstavlja vrednost vnosa preko vnosnega polja pripadajoče oznake obrazca (form-tag)"

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:81
msgid "A form-tag is a short code enclosed in square brackets used in a form content. A form-tag generally represents an input field, and its components can be separated into four parts: type, name, options, and values. Contact Form 7 supports several types of form-tags including text fields, number fields, date fields, checkboxes, radio buttons, menus, file-uploading fields, CAPTCHAs, and quiz fields."
msgstr "Obrazec-oznaka (form-tag) je kratka koda, zaprto v oglate oklepaje, ki se uporablja v vsebini obrazca. Oznaka obrazca običajno predstavlja vnosno polje katerega sestavni deli se lahko ločijo na štiri dele: vrsta, ime, možnosti in vrednosti. Contact Form 7 podpira več vrst oznak obrazca vključno z besedilnimi polji, številčna poljaj, polja z datumom, potrditvena polja, radio gumbi, meniji, CAPTCHA, polja za nalaganje datotek in kviz polja."

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:79
msgid "<strong>Additional Settings</strong> provides a place where you can customize the behavior of this contact form by adding code snippets."
msgstr "<strong>Dodatne nastavitve</strong> prostor kjer lahko prilagodite delovanje tega obrazca z dodajanjem kode."

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:78
msgid "In <strong>Messages</strong>, you can edit various types of messages used for this contact form. These messages are relatively short messages, like a validation error message you see when you leave a required field blank."
msgstr "V <strong>Sporočilih,</strong> lahko urejate različne vrste sporočil, ki se uporabljajo za ta kontaktni obrazec. Ta sporočila so kratka sporočila, kot  je naprimer sporočilo o napaki, ki se prikaže, ko pustite zahtevano polje prazno."

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:77
msgid "<strong>Mail (2)</strong> is an additional mail template that works similar to Mail. Mail (2) is different in that it is sent only when Mail has been sent successfully."
msgstr "<strong>Pošta (2)</strong> je dodatna poštna predloge, ki deluje podobno kot Pošta. Pošta (2) se razlikuje v tem, da se pošlje le, ko je bila Pošta uspešno poslana."

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:76
msgid "<strong>Mail</strong> manages a mail template (headers and message body) that this contact form will send when users submit it. You can use Contact Form 7&#8217;s mail-tags here."
msgstr "<strong>Pošta</strong> upravlja poštno predlogo (glave in telo sporočila), ki bo poslana s tem kontaktnim obrazcem, ki jo pošlje uporabniki. Tu lahko uporabite poštne-oznake Kontaktnega obrazca 7’"

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:75
msgid "<strong>Form</strong> is a content of HTML form. You can use arbitrary HTML, which is allowed inside a form element. You can also use Contact Form 7&#8217;s form-tags here."
msgstr "<strong>Obrazec</strong> je HTML vsebina obrazca. Uporabite lahko poljubni HTML, ki je dovoljen znotraj elementa obrazca. Tu lahko uporabite Contact Form 7 oznake obrazca (form-tags)"

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:74
msgid "<strong>Title</strong> is the title of a contact form. This title is only used for labeling a contact form, and can be edited."
msgstr "<strong>Naslovno ime</strong> je ime kontaktnega obrazca. To ime se uporablja samo za označevanje kontaktnega obrazca in ga lahko urejate."

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:73
msgid "On this screen, you can edit a contact form. A contact form is comprised of the following components:"
msgstr "V tem oknu lahko uredite kontaktni obrazec. Kontaktni obrazec je sestavljen iz naslednjih komponent:"

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:71
msgid "<strong>Duplicate</strong> - Clones that contact form. A cloned contact form inherits all content from the original, but has a different ID."
msgstr "<strong>Podvoji</strong> - Klonira ta kontaktni obrazec. Kloniran kontaktni obrazec podeduje vso vsebino originala ima le drug ID."

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:70
msgid "<strong>Edit</strong> - Navigates to the editing screen for that contact form. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the contact form title."
msgstr "<strong>Urejanje</strong> - Vas vodi na okno urejanja kontaktnega obrazca. To okno lahko odprete tudi tako, da kliknete na ime kontaktnega obrazca."

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:69
msgid "Hovering over a row in the contact forms list will display action links that allow you to manage your contact form. You can perform the following actions:"
msgstr "S postavitvijo kazalca na vrstico v seznamu kontaktnih obrazcev se vam prikažejo povezana dejanja, ki vam omogočajo upravljanje s kontaktnim obrazcem. Na voljo so vam sledeča dejanja:"

#: admin/includes/help-tabs.php:67
msgid "On this screen, you can manage contact forms provided by Contact Form 7. You can manage an unlimited number of contact forms. Each contact form has a unique ID and Contact Form 7 shortcode ([contact-form-7 ...]). To insert a contact form into a post or a text widget, insert the shortcode into the target."
msgstr "V tem oknu lahko upravljate kontaktne obrazce, ki jih zagotavlja Kontaktni obrazec 7. Lahko upravljate neomejeno število kontaktnih obrazcev. Vsak kontaktni obrazec ima edinstveno ime in kratko kodo ([contact-form-7 ...]). Če želite vstaviti kontaktni obrazec v objavo ali besedilni gradnik, vstavite kratko kodo v ustrezno mesto."

